title: GFRIEND Shares New Set Of Gorgeous Concept Photos For “Fingertip”
text:
Shares 146   
GFRIEND continues to rock their vintage military concept in their latest concept photos for their comeback! 
After releasing a set of individual and duo shots for their return yesterday , GFRIEND has now shared another batch of solo photos, in which the members look stunning in outfits that are inspired by both military dress uniforms and combat wear.
